* DATE		AUTHOR		DESCRIPTION
*-------------------------------------------------------------------
* 11/02/2006	VR	Changed data type smalldatetime to datetime to comply with maturity dates that 
*					are greater than the smalldatetime type will allow
* 02/20/2009	CC	Add entity level UDF and data_type = 'TABLE'
* 08/05/2009	SC	Added new error handling
* 08/08/2012	SC	Changed ps_id to psv_id
* 10/26/2012	SC	#3444 Fix for latest version of compliance
* 08/28/2013	SC	#3910 Increased table size to 8000
* 07/09/2014	SC	#5330 Increased table size to MAX
* 07/23/2015	SC	#4469 Added @force_float
* 02/15/2016	SC	#14623 Fix for layout fields
* 03/25/2021	TK	#163373. #175462. Fixed dynamic SQL when PS Layout includes columns from PS_Issue_Rating
* 08/20/2021	TK	#200168. #202783. Fixed/added column list when @command_mode = INSERT  
* 03/26/2026	HK	Field names starting with integers must be wrapped in square brackets to comply with SQL Server syntax rules.
